{
  "design_notes": "The chart is built for a medium difficulty, carefully scaling from a sparse intro with simple quarter-note steps into a syncopated build, and then standard eighth-note runs during the drops. To respect the 5.0 NPS sustained budget, eighth-note streams are intentionally broken with quarters and half-note rests. Holds are introduced on prominent vocal/synth sustains to provide a varied and engaging physical texture without exceeding the 15% budget. The drops feel driving but highly readable with minimal crossover strain.",
